description: Price Improvement! This stunning Southie condominium is located in a modern elevator building, with a thoughtfully designed floor plan that includes 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms! Beautiful kitchen with gas cooking, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious island that serves as both a casual dining area and additional workspace. The impressive primary suite easily fits a king-sized bed and boasts his-and-hers walk-in closets along with a large en-suite bathroom. The second bedroom, on the opposite end of the unit for added privacy, is ideal for a guest room or home office and is complemented by a generous second bathroom. This home offers all the modern conveniences expected at this level, located in one of the city's most desirable neighborhoods!
